Package
Description
co.edu.unbosque.controller
The package co.edu.unbosque.controller includes the classes that manage the main logic and the interaction between the different components of the system.
co.edu.unbosque.model
The package co.edu.unbosque.model contains the classes that define the data structure and represents the fundamental entities of the system.
co.edu.unbosque.model.persistence
The package co.edu.unbosque.model.persistence includes the classes in charge of managing data persistence in the system.
co.edu.unbosque.util
The package co.edu.unbosque.util provides implementations of fundamental utilities for data structure and common operations in the system.
co.edu.unbosque.util.exception
The package co.edu.unbosque.util.exception provides custom exceptions that are specific to handle errors related to data entry in the system.
co.edu.unbosque.view
The package co.edu.unbosque.view host the classes related to the user interface of the system.
